Repository Name Unauthorized: University of Tampa, Merl Kelce Library
Notes: Holds  UT archival documents (administrative, departmental, committee, institutional publications, et al.) as well as artifacts and information that reflect UT’s, Tampa’s, and west-central Florida’s history Collections including the papers of Stanley Kimmel, friend of Hemingway and noted Abraham Lincoln assassination and Booth family expert and  the papers of Blanche Yurka, opera star, Broadway and Hollywood  actress.
